title: OmniOS r151004 - Fall 2012 (omnios-33fdde4)
description:
The Fall 2012 release of OmniOS (r151004) a Solaris derived UNIX distribution.

Features:
 * Illumos Kernel
 * ZFS fileystsem
 * DTrace Analytics
 * KVM Hypervisor
 * Zones lightweight virtualization
 * IPS Package Management 

Learn more at: http://omnios.omniti.com/
